import React from 'react';
import {
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Routes,
  Route,
} from 'react-router-dom';
import Home from './pages/Home';

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Routes>
        {/* Authentification and Authorization */}
        <Route exact path='/login' element={ <Login /> } />
        <Route exact path='/signup' element={ <Registration /> } />

        {/* Main Pages */}
        <Route exact path='/' element={ <Navigate to='/login' /> } />
        <Route exact path='/dashboard' element={ <PrivateRoute /> }>
          <Route exact path='/dashboard' element={ <Dashboard /> } />
        </Route>
        <Route exact path='/profile' element={ <PrivateRoute /> }>
          <Route exact path='/profile' element={ <Profile /> } />
        </Route>
        <Route exact path='/analytics' element={ <PrivateRoute /> }>
          <Route exact path='/analytics' element={ <Analytics /> } />
        </Route>
        <Route exact path='/calendar' element={ <PrivateRoute /> }>
          <Route exact path='/calendar' element={ <Calendar /> } />
        </Route>
        <Route exact path='/publications' element={ <PrivateRoute /> }>
          <Route exact path='/publications' element={ <Publication /> } />
        </Route>
        <Route path='/publications/:uuid' element={ <PrivateRoute /> }>
          <Route path='/publications/:uuid' element={ <PublicationDetail /> } />
        </Route>
        <Route path='/publications/:uuid/image' element={ <PrivateRoute /> }>
          <Route path='/publications/:uuid/image' element={ <PublicationDetailImage /> } />
        </Route>
        <Route exact path='/feedback' element={ <PrivateRoute /> }>
          <Route exact path='/feedback' element={ <Feedback /> } />
        </Route>
        <Route path='/feedback/:uuid' element={ <PrivateRoute /> }>
          <Route path='/feedback/:uuid' element={ <FeedbackDetail /> } />
        </Route>
        <Route exact path='/support' element={ <PrivateRoute /> }>
          <Route exact path='/support' element={ <Support /> } />
        </Route>

        {/* NotFound Page */}
        <Route exact path='/not-found' element={ <NotFound /> } />
        <Route path='*' element={ <Navigate to='/not-found' /> } />
      </Routes>
    </Router>
  );
}

export default App;
